  <div id="text-content_0F0A87F0-2213-0135-2A39-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Link to a Question Bank</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="find_question_bank" data-step-uuid="A6B6F51F-E478-43D4-9F9C-BC99B581EA84">
