  <div id="text-content_0F0AD110-2213-0135-2A3B-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the question bank you want to reference in your quiz [1]. Click the <strong>Select Bank </strong>button<strong> </strong>[2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="create_group" data-step-uuid="908D99F8-4A16-4812-B02B-E3EAF5BBE2BA">
